{"tid":549772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[神既安排]男子上教會途中 鳴鳳街中伏被亂棍扑頭","createTime":"2018-02-04T04:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T05:28:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"505af920a65902b2473b3d92c747130c9ebdbf85","tid":549772,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"男子上教會途中 鳴鳳街中伏被亂棍扑頭<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙早上發生傷人案。一名姓黃(52歲)男子，駕駛七人車載同親友，抵達黃大仙竹園鳴鳳街，甫下車步往附近一教會途中，突然有3至4名南亞裔男子手持木棍趨近，將他拉往一邊，並以木棍襲擊及扑打其頭部，他寡不敵眾，受傷倒地。親友見狀大聲呼救，由途人協助致電報警。警員接報到場，兇徒已作鳥獸散，警方正調查對方逞兇動機。"},{"pid":"48209bc32489dfd45451ea740c6b4d1af12080f9","tid":549772,"uid":85819,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9a3f7a8c144a65176a5b0de924e2f4eaf1bae1d","tid":549772,"uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"48209bc32489dfd45451ea740c6b4d1af12080f9","tid":549772,"uid":85819,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"天父爸爸派人打鳩你一定有用意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cf0313cadf49cdaf343a4c908a54849545594e","tid":549772,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b9a3f7a8c144a65176a5b0de924e2f4eaf1bae1d","tid":549772,"uid":122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"48209bc32489dfd45451ea740c6b4d1af12080f9","tid":549772,"uid":85819,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"天父爸爸派人打鳩你一定有用意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"當頭棒喝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67024ccf70d169fdc538786f2fb5b62e0b885aed","tid":549772,"uid":29317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"放下屠刀 